    <item>
      <title>牙买加再次推动放弃英国君主制，成为共和国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/jamaica-renews-push-to-abandon-monarchy-become-a-full-republic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，牙买加提出一项法案，放弃查理三世国王作为其象征性国家元首的地位，并将这个加勒比国家转变为一个正式的共和国，英国君主制遭受打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/jamaica-renews-push-to-abandon-monarchy-become-a-full-republic</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 16:36:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税风险搅乱黄金和白银 纽约金价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/trump-tariff-risk-roils-gold-and-silver-as-new-york-prices-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员权衡美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提出的全面关税措施中包括贵金属的可能性，纽约黄金和白银期货的溢价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/trump-tariff-risk-roils-gold-and-silver-as-new-york-prices-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 16:09:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普定于周四敲响纽约证券交易所的开市钟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/trump-scheduled-to-ring-nyse-s-opening-bell-on-thursday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普定于周四敲响纽约证券交易所的开市钟，并在美国资本主义的标志性象征前为这位誓言要振兴美国经济的候任总统提供拍照庆祝的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/trump-scheduled-to-ring-nyse-s-opening-bell-on-thursday</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 15:54:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟支持对俄罗斯的制裁方案，并向斯洛伐克作出让步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/eu-backs-russian-sanctions-package-with-concession-to-slovakia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟初步支持针对俄罗斯的第 15 项制裁措施，其中包括将斯洛伐克从俄罗斯石油中提取的石油产品的贸易豁免期延长至 6 月初。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/eu-backs-russian-sanctions-package-with-concession-to-slovakia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 15:07:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>后阿萨德时代叙利亚武装头目的结局仍是个大谜团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/militant-leader-s-end-game-is-big-unknown-in-post-assad-syria</link>
      <description><![CDATA[驻大马士革的电视节目主持人兼制片人米雷拉·阿布·沙纳布走进叙利亚首都的一家糕点店，看到武装的伊斯兰战士正在吃冰淇淋和蛋糕。其中一人转过身问她是基督徒、德鲁兹派还是什叶派，以及这是否是她不戴面纱的原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/militant-leader-s-end-game-is-big-unknown-in-post-assad-syria</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 14:53:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国禁止患有性别焦虑症的 18 岁以下青少年使用青春期阻滞剂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/uk-bans-puberty-blockers-for-under-18s-with-gender-dysphoria</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府将无限期禁止为患有性别焦虑症的 18 岁以下青少年开青春期阻滞剂，英国成为欧洲最新一个对青少年性别肯定护理实施限制的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/uk-bans-puberty-blockers-for-under-18s-with-gender-dysphoria</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 14:37:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称俄罗斯可能在几天内向乌克兰发射奥列什尼克导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/us-says-russia-may-fire-oreshnick-missile-at-ukraine-in-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国官员称，俄罗斯可能在未来几天向乌克兰发射另一枚中程弹道导弹。]]></description>
