      <title>立法者考虑通过法案，强制药品中间商出售药房</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/lawmakers-plan-bill-forcing-drug-middlemen-to-sell-pharmacies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国两党议员联盟起草了一项法案，迫使处方药中间商剥离其拥有的药店。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/lawmakers-plan-bill-forcing-drug-middlemen-to-sell-pharmacies</guid>
