    <item>
      <title>特朗普会晤后奥尔班致电俄罗斯总统普京讨论乌克兰问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/orban-talks-with-russia-s-putin-on-ukraine-after-trump-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班周三致电俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京，这是他在与美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普会晤后就乌克兰战争展开的最新一轮外交行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/orban-talks-with-russia-s-putin-on-ukraine-after-trump-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 10:29:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约考虑成员国的新武器、装备目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/nato-weighs-new-weapons-equipment-targets-for-member-countries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情官员透露，北约计划对成员国需要生产多少坦克、飞机和其他武器系统设定新的具体目标，这可能需要将北约的国防开支目标提高到国内生产总值的 3%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/nato-weighs-new-weapons-equipment-targets-for-member-countries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 09:05:43 GMT</pubDate>
